{"tid":1650563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「有關今後所有行動」我想大家搞清楚咩叫核爆都唔割","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:54:41.000Z","uid":99805,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"952afdb019a87a3d4468cfa6b3e03b22f981f167","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔係淨係針對蛋榚事件，係所有on9野都應該割。<br />\n<br />\n我講既on9野要割係指果件事出<span style=\"color: red;\">發點係咪為場運動</span>，大家仲記唔記得雨革有人打牌？<br />\n屌你老母打牌，切蛋榚關場運動撚事咩？所有非光復香港有關既動作都一定要割<br />\n<br />\n唔好用班狗做例子，醫院打人比cctv影到，人地一樣割，我唔理佢地割既出發點係乜野，總之我地呢邊，唔係為場運動既任何舉動都要割"},{"pid":"c0d9a8224e5d59f38056d6ad70f50fcb385c2d5a","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85eae11e229c173cd1ad155893eb17bc7f83e2ac","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6860d10965b2ba55658d0ecc06912125ae0d95a3","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9e61d7ccbc1eb68282bcc0ded0069e6dd167c5","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f476c864a3560e7f3c6470bb2f5dc101fc7bc16","tid":1650563,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac16ef3b70b3b7f88dfd44cf01de250bca6e535c","tid":1650563,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: